{"type":"message","id":"fd5818ed","parentId":"2897c74a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:13:57.335Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dh6id0n2f0zj_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5217\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1087\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[master 130ea94] pulse: 2026-03-24 001328\n 7 files changed, 295 insertions(+), 133 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 001328.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 001328.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 001230.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 001328 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step for Phase 1 advancement. I need to implement the classifier that will test the hypothesis that causal structure IS invariant structure.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"good-zephyr","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5217\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=1087\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[master 130ea94] pulse: 2026-03-24 001328\n 7 files changed, 295 insertions(+), 133 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 001328.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 001328.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 001230.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 001328 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next concrete step for Phase 1 advancement. I need to implement the classifier that will test the hypothesis that causal structure IS invariant structure.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774325637332}}
